OL,3,CLondon Marathon to take place over two
OL,4,Cdays in 2027 with 100,000 runners
OL,6,FNext year's London Marathon is set to
OL,7,Ftake place over two days and welcome
OL,8,Falmost double the number of usual
OL,9,Frunners, it has been confirmed.
OL,11,FA record-breaking 100,000 people will
OL,12,Fhave the chance to take part in 2027
OL,13,Fover the weekend of April 24 and 25.
OL,15,FThis year saw 59,830 people finish the
OL,16,FLondon Marathon, out of 60,512
OL,17,Fparticipants.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
