OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781858896
OL,3,CLondon Marathon to take place over two
OL,4,Cdays in 2027 with 100,000 runners
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"London is the sporting capital of the
OL,12,Fworld and I am delighted that, for one
OL,13,Fyear only in 2027, the world famous
OL,14,FTCS London Marathon will expand into a
OL,15,Ftwo-day event," London mayor Sadiq
OL,16,FKhan said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
