OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781858896
OL,3,CLondon Marathon to take place over two
OL,4,Cdays in 2027 with 100,000 runners
OL,6,F"This unique, one-off double will
OL,7,Fallow a record 100,000 participants to
OL,8,Ftake part across the two days `
OL,9,Fcreating the largest fundraising
OL,10,Fmoment in UK sporting history and
OL,11,Fsupporting the work of so many
OL,12,Fincredible charities.
OL,14,F"The London Marathon showcases the
OL,15,Fvery best of our capital and we will
OL,16,Fcontinue working closely with London
OL,17,FMarathon Events and our partners to
OL,18,Fensure appropriate measures are in
OL,19,Fplace for the entire weekend as we
OL,20,Fbuild a better, more prosperous London
OL,21,Ffor everyone."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
