OL,3,CLondon Marathon to take place over two
OL,4,Cdays in 2027 with 100,000 runners
OL,6,FLondon Marathon organisers were
OL,7,Freported to be exploring the
OL,8,Fpossibility of staging the event
OL,9,Facross two days earlier this year.
OL,11,FA record 1.33million people have
OL,12,Falready applied for the 2027 edition
OL,13,Fof the race - a 36% year-on-year
OL,14,Fincrease - and the ballots will be
OL,15,Fchosen in July.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
