OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781858896
OL,3,CLondon Marathon to take place over two
OL,4,Cdays in 2027 with 100,000 runners
OL,6,FElite women, elite female para-
OL,7,Fathletes, championship and 'good for
OL,8,Fage' women will compete on one day,
OL,9,Fand their male equivalents on the
OL,10,Fother, but the exact details are yet
OL,11,Fto be confirmed.
OL,13,FOrganisers have set aside two
OL,14,Fguaranteed entries for teachers and
OL,15,Fstaff at every school in the capital,
OL,16,Fand entries have also been allocated
OL,17,Fto every London borough along the
OL,18,Froute.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
