OL,3,CLondon Marathon to take place over two
OL,4,Cdays in 2027 with 100,000 runners
OL,6,FThe 2026 London Marathon was the site
OL,7,Fof multiple milestones, including
OL,8,FSabastian Sawe's world-record breaking
OL,9,Fone hour, 59 minutes and 30 seconds
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,FBoth Sawe, from Kenya, and Yomif
OL,13,FKejelcha of Ethiopia broke the two-
OL,14,Fhour barrier for the first time in
OL,15,Fhistory.
OL,17,FMore than #90million was raised for
OL,18,Fcharity by participants, a figure
OL,19,Forganisers hope will be much higher as
OL,20,Fa result of expanded capacity across
OL,21,Ftwo days.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
