OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781858896
OL,3,CLondon Marathon to take place over two
OL,4,Cdays in 2027 with 100,000 runners
OL,6,FLondon Marathon CEO Hugh Brasher
OL,7,Festimates that more than #150million
OL,8,Fcan be raised and said the UK will
OL,9,Fbenefit from #400million in social and
OL,10,Feconomic benefit.
OL,12,F"The 2027 TCS London Marathon Double
OL,13,Fis our most ambitious evolution to
OL,14,Fdate ` a once-in-a-generation one-time-
OL,15,Fonly reimagining of what a marathon
OL,16,Fand city-wide celebration of activity
OL,17,Fcan be," Brasher said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
